00:35:45,140 --> 00:35:46,867
Good. There's still plenty of time.

833
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:49,320
What do you mean ‘plenty of time'?

834
00:35:49,470 --> 00:35:50,990
Today's already the 25th.

835
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,480
Huh?

836
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:54,036
It's the 25th already?

837
00:35:54,061 --> 00:35:54,590
Mm.

838
00:35:54,627 --> 00:35:55,627
What?

839
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,347
It feels like I just paid for it.

840
00:35:57,660 --> 00:35:59,994
If it's too expensive, I can transfer
to another school. I don't mind.

841
00:36:00,018 --> 00:36:01,249
No, you don't have to.

842
00:36:01,890 --> 00:36:03,458
Just work hard in school.

843
00:36:03,660 --> 00:36:05,624
Leave the money to me, got it?

844
00:36:12,490 --> 00:36:13,846
Yeah, I'm hurrying.

845
00:36:13,883 --> 00:36:15,532
My car is still being fixed.

846
00:36:15,858 --> 00:36:17,850
Just hang around while you wait for me.

847
00:36:18,110 --> 00:36:19,563
Like I wait for you every time.

848
00:36:19,606 --> 00:36:20,606
I have to go.

849
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,258
Hello.

850
00:36:24,289 --> 00:36:25,187
Toto Service.

851
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:27,255
Happy to serve with my life.

852
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:30,135
Today, I'm on duty to
drop you off at work, sir.

853
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:35,636
I don't like that.

854
00:36:35,655 --> 00:36:36,655
Can I do it again?

855
00:36:38,250 --> 00:36:39,458
Toto Service.

856
00:36:39,495 --> 00:36:41,249
Get anywhere fast the way you like it.

857
00:36:41,286 --> 00:36:43,240
I'm on duty to drop you off at work, sir.

858
00:36:47,930 --> 00:36:50,215
Your men were the ones causing trouble.

859
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:51,716
Are you really taking
all the responsibility?

860
00:36:51,735 --> 00:36:53,421
I'm the self-sacrificing type.

861
00:36:53,464 --> 00:36:55,420
As the leader, I have
to take responsibility.

862
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:59,298
Besides, working with someone
as picky as you

863
00:36:59,329 --> 00:37:00,824
is something only I can handle.

864
00:37:01,490 --> 00:37:03,329
We'll see if you can handle it.

865
00:37:03,384 --> 00:37:05,539
Where's the car you're using
to take me to the airport?

866
00:37:05,563 --> 00:37:09,003
Don't worry. I prepared a royal ride
worthy of your status.

867
00:37:09,033 --> 00:37:10,033
This way, please.

868
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:14,775
THE WINNERS RESCUE FOUNDATION

869
00:37:14,812 --> 00:37:15,489
Hey!

870
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:17,480
Did you bring a body transport car
to pick me up?

871
00:37:17,507 --> 00:37:18,516
Exactly.

872
00:37:18,541 --> 00:37:21,403
I was worried you'd be late for work,
so I came as fast as I could.

873
00:37:21,790 --> 00:37:22,498
Hey!

874
00:37:22,516 --> 00:37:24,221
There's actually a body inside!

875
00:37:24,252 --> 00:37:24,886
Of course.

876
00:37:24,935 --> 00:37:25,870
It's a body transport car.

877
00:37:25,913 --> 00:37:27,778
What were you expecting, minced pork?

878
00:37:27,796 --> 00:37:29,385
I think the person has
been dead for 10 days.

879
00:37:29,409 --> 00:37:30,695
There are so many worms

880
00:37:30,732 --> 00:37:31,993
crawling all over the body.

881
00:37:32,036 --> 00:37:33,723
The smell is really strong.

882
00:37:34,650 --> 00:37:36,055
Get in and see for yourself.

883
00:37:36,080 --> 00:37:36,892
I'm getting a taxi.

884
00:37:36,923 --> 00:37:37,938
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

885
00:37:37,956 --> 00:37:39,507
What taxi? I came all the way here.

886
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:39,981
Get in.

887
00:37:40,018 --> 00:37:40,720
No way!

888
00:37:40,750 --> 00:37:41,833
I owe you money.

889
00:37:41,860 --> 00:37:42,560
Let me hurry up and work it off
in this lifetime.

890
00:37:42,590 --> 00:37:43,661
No, I'm not going.

891
00:37:43,698 --> 00:37:44,633
Let's go.

892
00:37:44,658 --> 00:37:45,790
No way!

893
00:37:45,821 --> 00:37:46,529
No, I'm not going!

894
00:37:46,553 --> 00:37:47,553
Hey! No!

895
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:49,796
Open the door!

896
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,070
Open it!

897
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:56,086
Hey, drive carefully!

898
00:37:56,650 --> 00:37:58,130
I don't want to become the next body.

899
00:37:58,560 --> 00:38:02,818
You know nothing. So many people
would kill to be my passenger princess.

900
00:38:02,849 --> 00:38:03,809
Who would even want that?

901
00:38:03,827 --> 00:38:05,113
Count me out.

902
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:07,464
You don't need to pick me up again.

903
00:38:07,513 --> 00:38:09,390
Just find another way to pay me back.

904
00:38:09,415 --> 00:38:10,467
Okay, fine.

905
00:38:11,090 --> 00:38:12,996
If this is not thrilling enough,

906
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:16,498
I'll take you to do something
even more thrilling.

907
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:22,061
If you don't want my pick-up
and drop-off service,

908
00:38:22,098 --> 00:38:25,372
allow me to help you relax instead.

909
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:27,987
A friend of mine owns this massage place.

910
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:30,332
I'll give you a free session today.

911
00:38:30,740 --> 00:38:32,738
Take off your clothes and lie down.

912
00:38:32,781 --> 00:38:34,467
Do I really have to take off my shirt?

913
00:38:34,492 --> 00:38:35,064
Yeah.

914
00:38:35,390 --> 00:38:37,298
Maybe just massage over my clothes.

915
00:38:37,310 --> 00:38:38,178
I don't trust you.

916
00:38:38,221 --> 00:38:38,947
Please.

917
00:38:38,984 --> 00:38:40,940
You don't have to guard
your body that much.

918
00:38:40,978 --> 00:38:42,412
It's not like I'm even
that attracted to you.

919
00:38:42,436 --> 00:38:43,483
You're not my type.

920
00:38:47,020 --> 00:38:48,020
Come on!

921
00:38:49,180 --> 00:38:50,424
Right there.

922
00:38:51,300 --> 00:38:52,300
How are you feeling?

923
00:38:52,570 --> 00:38:53,570
Good?

924
00:38:53,850 --> 00:38:54,996
Yes, right there.

925
00:38:55,021 --> 00:38:56,110
So good.

926
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,080
Oh.

927
00:38:59,470 --> 00:39:00,787
Mm.

928
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,941
Oh.

929
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:05,280
So good.

930
00:39:05,660 --> 00:39:07,132
It's getting even better.

931
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:09,772
I guarantee it'll hit the spot.

932
00:39:18,650 --> 00:39:20,529
Hey! What are you doing?

933
00:39:20,553 --> 00:39:21,963
What are you doing?

934
00:39:22,740 --> 00:39:24,123
B to B, of course.

935
00:39:24,147 --> 00:39:25,452
Body to body.

936
00:39:25,870 --> 00:39:27,520
I'm going this far for you.

937
00:39:27,563 --> 00:39:29,163
You better cut my debt down a lot, okay?

938
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,196
Cut what?

939
00:39:30,209 --> 00:39:31,335
I want no more of this!

940
00:39:31,384 --> 00:39:32,849
That's enough. Stop.

941
00:39:32,886 --> 00:39:34,012
No!

942
00:39:34,049 --> 00:39:35,716
I'm about to show you my signature move.

943
00:39:35,741 --> 00:39:36,981
Reaching into the Dragon's Den.

944
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:38,603
Hey, no!

945
00:39:39,010 --> 00:39:39,760
Stop!

946
00:39:39,803 --> 00:39:43,267
Nooooo!

947
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:54,867
Hello, Lion.

948
00:39:54,898 --> 00:39:55,898
Where are you?

949
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:59,556
(I'm at home sick, lying in bed.)

950
00:39:59,581 --> 00:40:00,990
Oh? Really?

951
00:40:01,046 --> 00:40:01,692
Do you want me to come over?

952
00:40:01,723 --> 00:40:02,843
Have you taken any medicine?

953
00:40:03,175 --> 00:40:05,170
(It's okay. You don't have to come.)

954
00:40:05,224 --> 00:40:07,796
(I don't want you
catching the virus from me.)

955
00:40:07,821 --> 00:40:10,073
(I just need some
rest and I'll feel better.)

956
00:40:10,110 --> 00:40:11,255
(I'll see you later, okay?)

957
00:40:11,630 --> 00:40:13,784
Okay. Get plenty of rest.

958
00:40:20,090 --> 00:40:21,730
We turn left at this intersection, right?

959
00:40:24,860 --> 00:40:28,123
Sorry, can we turn right instead?

960
00:40:28,166 --> 00:40:30,036
I want to stop by my partner's place.

961
00:40:31,350 --> 00:40:31,969
Sure.

962
00:40:32,330 --> 00:40:33,330
Thank you.

963
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:39,550
Thank you.

964
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,120
Hey!

965
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:53,080
Lion!

966
00:40:54,330 --> 00:40:55,330
Hey!

967
00:41:07,580 --> 00:41:08,615
Could it be his birthday?

968
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:19,830
Hey, Lion.

969
00:41:21,870 --> 00:41:22,870
Lion!

970
00:41:38,570 --> 00:41:39,600
Hello, Lion.

971
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:42,104
How are you feeling?

972
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:44,172
(I'm still not feeling very well.)

973
00:41:44,756 --> 00:41:46,196
(I'm in my room sick, lying in bed.)

974
00:41:48,060 --> 00:41:49,243
Which room?

975
00:41:50,810 --> 00:41:53,372
(Well… my bedroom at home, of course.)

976
00:41:54,110 --> 00:41:55,110
But…

977
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:58,953
(Kanit, is something wrong?)

978
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:02,283
Oh, it's nothing.

979
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:06,140
Don't forget to take your medicine.

980
00:42:06,500 --> 00:42:07,606
Get well soon.

981
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:08,800
(Okay.)

982
00:42:09,050 --> 00:42:12,116
(I'm going to get some sleep.
(I'm really not feeling well.)

983
00:42:12,510 --> 00:42:13,600
Bye.

984
00:42:18,750 --> 00:42:21,618
Tomorrow morning, I have to wake
up early for a wedding in Phang Nga.

985
00:42:21,643 --> 00:42:24,221
I might…

986
00:42:24,710 --> 00:42:25,729
not be able to go with you anymore.

987
00:42:25,753 --> 00:42:27,396
My friend needs help,

988
00:42:27,421 --> 00:42:28,836
so I have to cover his flight.

989
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:40,381
We're heading out.

990
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:41,723
Mm.

991
00:42:41,784 --> 00:42:43,243
Once I'm done fixing
this, I'll head out too.

992
00:42:43,267 --> 00:42:43,753
See you.

993
00:42:43,790 --> 00:42:44,295
See you, bro.

994
00:42:44,332 --> 00:42:44,990
See you.

995
00:42:45,130 --> 00:42:46,812
(Calling Polca 01.)

996
00:42:47,260 --> 00:42:48,996
(A cat is stuck on the roof of a house)

997
00:42:49,015 --> 00:42:50,818
(in Charan Soi 91.)

998
00:42:50,849 --> 00:42:52,449
(We need you on-site ASAP.)

999
00:42:53,050 --> 00:42:54,431
Do you seriously not have any other team?

1000
00:42:54,455 --> 00:42:56,006
(If I did, would I be calling you?)

1001
00:42:56,036 --> 00:42:57,156
(Go help them out.)

1002
00:42:57,181 --> 00:42:58,867
(That family donated a lot to us.)

1003
00:42:59,240 --> 00:43:00,240
Alright.

1004
00:43:03,980 --> 00:43:04,980
Let's go.

1005
00:43:06,307 --> 00:43:08,449
We're on standby 24/7 anyway.

1006
00:43:27,741 --> 00:43:28,741
Hey!

1007
00:43:29,030 --> 00:43:30,313
Hey, hey, hey!

1008
00:43:30,344 --> 00:43:31,344
Hey!

1009
00:43:32,400 --> 00:43:33,932
Excuse me, can you follow that car?

1010
00:43:33,963 --> 00:43:34,369
Oh.

1011
00:43:34,570 --> 00:43:35,570
Okay.

1012
00:43:40,055 --> 00:43:41,052
Hey! Hey!

1013
00:43:41,076 --> 00:43:42,086
Pull over!

1014
00:43:42,570 --> 00:43:43,570
Hey!

1015
00:43:45,255 --> 00:43:47,566
By the time we get there, that cat
might've already come down from the tree.

1016
00:43:47,590 --> 00:43:49,292
Hey! Hey! Pull over!

1017
00:43:49,790 --> 00:43:50,790
Hey!

1018
00:43:50,910 --> 00:43:51,606
I have something urgent!

1019
00:43:51,753 --> 00:43:53,636
Can you call the boss
and say we'll be late?

1020
00:43:53,673 --> 00:43:54,673
Yeah, okay.

1021
00:43:55,240 --> 00:43:56,320
Let me text him real quick.

1022
00:43:57,560 --> 00:43:58,923
Stop the car!

1023
00:43:59,120 --> 00:44:00,566
I have something urgent
to talk to you about!

1024
00:44:00,584 --> 00:44:01,230
Hey!

1025
00:44:01,550 --> 00:44:01,858
Hey!

1026
00:44:01,876 --> 00:44:03,427
Cats stress me out more than people do.

1027
00:44:03,446 --> 00:44:04,153
Damn it.

1028
00:44:04,178 --> 00:44:05,379
I'm not even this stressed over people.

1029
00:44:05,403 --> 00:44:08,172
Hey, go cut them off up ahead.

1030
00:44:08,196 --> 00:44:09,415
You got it, boss!

1031
00:44:10,120 --> 00:44:11,120
Hey!

1032
00:44:14,530 --> 00:44:16,129
Hey! Hey! Stop!

1033
00:44:16,153 --> 00:44:16,707
Stop!

1034
00:44:16,732 --> 00:44:17,347
Hey!

1035
00:44:17,372 --> 00:44:18,449
Stop!

1036
00:44:19,210 --> 00:44:20,670
Hey, why did you stop the car?

1037
00:44:22,230 --> 00:44:23,963
Get out and talk to your rival.

1038
00:44:30,700 --> 00:44:31,735
Hey!

1039
00:44:32,350 --> 00:44:34,990
Do you want to die? Is that why
you're blocking the rescue vehicle?

1040
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:36,440
What's this?

1041
00:44:36,510 --> 00:44:37,668
Did you come to collect the debt?

1042
00:44:37,692 --> 00:44:38,633
Isn't this too much?

1043
00:44:38,670 --> 00:44:41,058
Please just let me work. I'm begging you.

1044
00:44:41,083 --> 00:44:42,376
I'm not here to collect your debt.

1045
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:44,621
I've figured out how you can repay me.

1046
00:44:44,940 --> 00:44:46,252
Is this really the time?

1047
00:44:46,295 --> 00:44:47,883
Can't you see I'm in a hurry?

1048
00:44:47,913 --> 00:44:49,360
I can't wait.

1049
00:44:49,396 --> 00:44:51,230
I'm too anxious. It has to be now.

1050
00:44:51,273 --> 00:44:52,363
What is it? Make it quick.

1051
00:44:52,400 --> 00:44:53,520
I have to go save a cat.

1052
00:44:54,740 --> 00:44:58,258
I need you to investigate
my boyfriend's cheating.

1053
00:44:58,730 --> 00:44:59,730
What?

1054
00:45:00,210 --> 00:45:02,258
I just caught my boyfriend lying to me.

1055
00:45:02,750 --> 00:45:07,009
And I remember you just helped your friend
investigate their cheating partner too.

1056
00:45:07,870 --> 00:45:08,701
I knew it.

1057
00:45:08,726 --> 00:45:10,301
You dared to risk your life

1058
00:45:10,970 --> 00:45:12,450
because your man's going to dump you.

1059
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:13,760
How about this?

1060
00:45:14,250 --> 00:45:15,427
If I help you with this,

1061
00:45:16,260 --> 00:45:17,569
can we consider my debt paid?

1062
00:45:17,587 --> 00:45:21,230
If you can prove it with evidence,

1063
00:45:21,710 --> 00:45:24,412
I might consider forgiving your debt.

1064
00:45:25,120 --> 00:45:26,227
Then don't worry.

1065
00:45:26,566 --> 00:45:28,560
Other people's business
is my area of expertise,

1066
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:29,969
Mr. Boiling Tofu.

1067
00:45:31,300 --> 00:45:32,836
Just don't be all bark and no bite.

1068
00:45:33,187 --> 00:45:34,701
I need results too,

1069
00:45:35,770 --> 00:45:37,476
Mr. Black-Smoke Barking Dog.

1070
00:45:39,858 --> 00:45:41,058
You'll see.

1071
00:45:42,510 --> 00:45:44,160
I'm not all talk.

1072
00:45:55,360 --> 00:45:56,360
Be careful.

1073
00:46:08,240 --> 00:46:09,138
Hey, bro.

1074
00:46:09,175 --> 00:46:10,184
Stop flirting.

1075
00:46:10,209 --> 00:46:11,267
That cat is waiting.

1076
00:46:12,900 --> 00:46:13,900
Who's flirting?

1077
00:46:13,960 --> 00:46:15,336
Why would I even flirt
with someone who looks like this?

1078
00:46:15,360 --> 00:46:16,520
You're not even good-looking.

1079
00:46:33,490 --> 00:46:35,956
(Next Episode)
What about catching my boyfriend cheating?

1080
00:46:36,100 --> 00:46:38,153
Don't worry. I'll take care of it.

1081
00:46:38,170 --> 00:46:39,907
I'll open your eyes

1082
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:41,200
to your boyfriend's true colors.

1083
00:46:42,380 --> 00:46:43,667
He's a lying piece of shit.

1084
00:46:45,100 --> 00:46:46,781
People usually sneak off to clubs.

1085
00:46:46,812 --> 00:46:47,852
He sneaks off to a temple.

1086
00:46:49,880 --> 00:46:50,880
Kanit.

1087
00:46:51,090 --> 00:46:52,831
If you have to doubt
your partner like this,

1088
00:46:52,855 --> 00:46:54,307
you'll never be happy.

